          <Link href="https://x.com/writendquit" external class="hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Security</Link> Research<br/>
          <span class="text-foreground">& <Link href="https://ctftime.org/user/233116" external class="hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">CTF</Link> Player</span>
        </h1>
        
        <!-- Intro -->
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-[15px] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Hi, <span class="text-foreground font-medium">:wq!</span> [colonwq] is a <Link href="https://x.com/writendquit" external class="text-foreground underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">security researcher</Link>, <Link href="https://ctftime.org/user/233116" external class="text-foreground underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">CTF player</Link>, 
          jailbreaking AI models & reverse engineering them to yield results in research, CTF, and bug bounties.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-[15px] leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Having keen interest in <span class="text-foreground">reverse engineering</span> and 
          <span class="text-foreground">binary exploitation</span> ‚Äî breaking things to understand how they work.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Status Toggle Switch - Clickable -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6">
          <button id="status-toggle" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2.5 border border-border rounded-full bg-background hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
